\c 8
\s UEzra ufundela abantu umlayo
\p
\v 1 Bonke abantu basebebuthana njengamuntu munye\x + Ezra 3.1.\x* egcekeni eliphambi kwesango lamanzi\x + 3.26.\x*; bakhuluma kuEzra umbhali ukuletha ugwalo lomlayo kaMozisi, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwulaye uIsrayeli\x + Ezra 7.6.\x*.
\v 2 UEzra umpristi wasewuletha umlayo phambi kwebandla, kusukela kowesilisa kusiya kowesifazana\x + Dute. 31.11,12.\x*, laye wonke owaqedisisa ukuzwa, ngosuku lokuqala lwenyanga yesikhombisa\x + 8.9. Levi 23.24.\x*.
\v 3 Wasebala kuwo phambi kwegceke\x + Dute. 31.11,12.\x* eliphambi kwesango lamanzi kusukela emadabukakusa kwaze kwaba semini enkulu, phambi kwabesilisa labesifazana labaqedisisayo; lendlebe zabo bonke abantu zazingasegwalweni lomlayo\x + 3.26.\x*.
\v 4 UEzra umbhali wasesima phezu kwendawo ephakemeyo yamapulanka ababeyenzele loludaba. Leceleni kwakhe kwakumi oMathithiya loShema\x + Ezra 10.43.\x* loAnaya\x + 10.22.\x* loUriya\x + Ezra 8.33.\x* loHilikhiya loMahaseya ngakwesokunene sakhe\x + 8.7. 3.23. 10.25. 11.5. 12.41,42. Ezra 10.21,22. Ezra 10.18,30.\x*; langakwesokhohlo sakhe oPhedaya, loMishayeli, loMalikiya\x + 3.11,14,31. 10.3. 12.42. Ezra 10.25,31.\x*, loHashuma\x + 10.18. Ezra 2.19.\x*, loHashibadana, uZekhariya\x + Ezra 8.16.\x*, uMeshulamu\x + Ezra 8.16.\x*.
\v 5 UEzra wasevula ugwalo phambi kwamehlo abo bonke abantu; ngoba wayengaphezu kwabantu bonke\x + 8.4.\x*; lapho eluvula, bonke abantu basukuma.
\v 6 UEzra waseyibusisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu omkhulu\x + Josh. 22.33.\x*. Bonke abantu basebephendula \add bathi\add*: Ameni, ameni\x + 5.13.\x*, ngokuphakamisa izandla zabo\x + Hlab. 134.2. Lilo 3.41. 1 Tim. 2.8.\x*; basebekhothama, bayikhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* ngobuso emhlabathini\x + 2 Lan. 20.18.\x*.
\v 7 OJeshuwa\x + Ezra 2.40.\x*, loBani\x + Ezra 2.10.\x*, loSherebiya\x + Ezra 8.18.\x*, uJamini, uAkubi, uShabethayi\x + Ezra 10.15.\x*, uHodiya\x + 9.5. 10.10,13.\x*, uMahaseya\x + 8.7. 3.23. 10.25. 11.5. 12.41,42. Ezra 10.21,22. Ezra 10.18,30.\x*, uKelita\x + Ezra 10.23.\x*, uAzariya\x + 3.23.\x*, uJozabadi\x + Ezra 8.33.\x*, uHanani\x + 10.10.\x*, uPelaya\x + 10.10.\x*, lamaLevi basebesenza abantu baqedisise umlayo\x + 2 Lan. 35.3.\x*, abantu besendaweni yabo\x + 9.3.\x*.
\v 8 Basebebala egwalweni, emlayweni kaNkulunkulu, ngokucacileyo, bechasisa, be\add b\add*enza \add ba\add*zwisise ekubaleni\x + Ezra 4.18.\x*.
\p
\v 9 UNehemiya owayengumbusi, lompristi uEzra umbhali, lamaLevi ayefundisa abantu\x + 8.7,8,12.\x*, basebesithi ebantwini bonke: Lolusuku lungcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 8.2.\x*; lingalili njalo lingakhali inyembezi. Ngoba bonke abantu bakhala inyembezi lapho besizwa amazwi omlayo\x + Tshu. 3.4.\x*.
\v 10 Wasesithi kibo: Hambani, lidle okunonileyo, linathe okumnandi, lithumele izabelo kongalungiselwanga lutho; ngoba lolusuku lungcwele eNkosini yethu, njalo lingadabuki, ngoba intokozo yeN\nd kosi\nd* ingamandla enu.
\v 11 AmaLevi asebathulisa bonke abantu esithi: Thulani, ngoba lolusuku lungcwele, lingadabuki.
\v 12 Bonke abantu basebehamba uku\add ya\add*kudla, lokunatha, lokuthumela izabelo\x + 8.12. Esta 9.22.\x*, lokwenza intokozo enkulu, ngoba babewaqedisisile amazwi ababebazise wona\x + 8.7-9.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Langosuku lwesibili kwabuthana inhloko zaboyise zabo bonke abantu, abapristi, lamaLevi, kuEzra umbhali\x + 8.1.\x*, ukuze baqedisise amazwi omlayo.
\v 14 Basebethola kubhaliwe emlayweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwulayile ngesandla sikaMozisi ukuthi abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahlale emadumbeni ngomkhosi ngenyanga yesikhombisa\x + Levi 23.34,42. Dute. 16.13.\x*,
\v 15 lokuthi bazwakalise bedlulise isimemezelo kuyo yonke imizi yabo\x + 12.42. Levi 23.4.\x* laseJerusalema\x + Dute. 16.16.\x* besithi: Phumelani entabeni lilethe ingatsha zezihlahla zemihlwathi, lengatsha zezihlahla zamafutha, lengatsha zezihlahla \w zamamiteli\w**\x + 1 Kho. 6.23.\x*, lengatsha zamalala\x + Levi 23.40.\x*, lengatsha zezihlahla ezilamahlamvu aminyeneyo, ukwenza amadumba, njengokubhaliweyo\x + Levi 23.40.\x*.
\v 16 Basebephuma abantu, baziletha, bazenzela amadumba, ngulowo lalowo ephahleni lwakhe, lemagumeni abo, lemagumeni endlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 2 Sam. 11.2.\x*, legcekeni lesango lamanzi\x + 8.1,3. 3.26.\x*, legcekeni lesango lakoEfrayimi\x + 12.39. 2 Kho. 14.13. 2 Lan. 25.23.\x*.
\v 17 Ibandla lonke lalabo ababebuyile ekuthunjweni basebesenza amadumba, bahlala emadumbeni. Ngoba kusukela ensukwini zikaJoshuwa indodana kaNuni kwaze kwaba yilolosuku abantwana bakoIsrayeli babengenzanga njalo\x + 1 Kho. 8.2. 2 Lan. 7.9. 8.13. Ezra 3.4.\x*. Kwasekusiba lentokozo enkulu kakhulu\x + 2 Lan. 30.21.\x*.
\v 18 Njalo usuku ngosuku kusukela osukwini lokuqala kwaze kwaba lusuku lokucina wabala egwalweni lomlayo kaNkulunkulu. Bawenza-ke umkhosi insuku eziyisikhombisa; kwathi ngosuku lwesificaminwembili kwaba lenhlangano enzulu, njengesimiso\x + Dute. 31.10,11.\x*.